data.description: Discover a blend of classic charm and modern upgrades in this single-family home nestled in the heart of Ocoee, FL. Built-in 1959 and renovated in 2020, this residence offers a foundation of quality with room for your personal enhancements.    Step inside to appreciate the new ceramic tile floors and an open-concept design that unites the family, dining, and kitchen areas. The updated kitchen boasts white cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Four bedrooms and two remodeled bathrooms provide ample space for comfort.    The exterior, freshly painted, complements a new roof and updated electrical panels. Enjoy the perks of no HOA and the proximity to local parks and Starke Lake.    This Ocoee gem is perfect for those looking for a place to call home    Call to schedule a showing today!
